			<section class="qaitem" js-foldable-group="internet">
				<div class="qaitem-title" role="button" tabindex="0" js-foldable-head>
					<h5 class="qaitem-title-txt  h3 h3-mb text-dark fw-bold">
						Q1: What is CUBC Merchant app, and how can it benefit my business?
					</h5>
				</div>
				<div class="qaitem-detail" js-foldable-body>
					<div class="qaitem-detail-content">
						<div class="badge badge-green h5 h5-mb mb-3">Answer</div>
						<p>
							The CUBC Merchant App simplifies business management by enabling secure digital payment acceptances, cashier control, and sales tracking. You can generate QR codes, manage cashier across branches, receive instant payment notifications, and monitor transactions effortlessly &mdash; all in one app.
						</p>
