					<div class="qaitem-detail-content">
						<div class="badge badge-green h5 h5-mb mb-3">Answer</div>
						<p class="mb-2">You can download to display or generate a QR code directly from the app for customers to scan and complete their payment. The app offers two types of QR codes: </p>
						<ul class="list-disc">
							<li>Static QR &mdash; Customers manually enter the payment amount after scanning</li>
							<li>Dynamic QR &mdash; The payment amount is pre-entered in the QR code, so customers only need to scan and confirm.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>


			<!-- QA item -->
